<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Ai Tutor</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.0.0-alpha1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-r4NyP46KrjDleawBgD5tp8Y7UzmLA05oM1iAEQ17CSuDqnUK2+k9luXQOfXJCJ4I" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.0.0-alpha1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-oesi62hOLfzrys4LxRF63OJCXdXDipiYWBnvTl9Y9/TRlw5xlKIEHpNyvvDShgf/" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <style>
  .main{
    max-width: 960px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  header{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(#2C6E49, #4CAF50);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #121212;
    box-shadow: 0px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }
  .sectionimg img{
    width: 100%;
    transform: scale(0.99);
    max-height: 85vh;
    filter: blur(1.7px);
    transition: 0.3s;
  }
  .sectionimg img:hover{
   transform: scale(1.001);
   filter: blur(1px);
  }
  .content{
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
    color: white !important;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px;
    filter: drop-shadow(0px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3));
  }
  .content h2,.content h3{
    padding: 5px;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px #121212;
  }
  .content button{
    padding: 2px 10px;
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(#4CAF50,#58cc8a);
    border: 1px solid #121212;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .main-content{
    padding: 30px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .line{
    background: #2C6E49;
    height: 3px;
   width:60px;
  }
  p{
    text-align: justify;
  }
  .start{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .start button{
    padding: 2px 10px;
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(#4CAF50,#58cc8a);
    border: 1px solid #121212;
    border-radius: 4px;

  }
  footer{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(#2C6E49, #4CAF50);
   color: white !important;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #121212;
    box-shadow: 0px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }
  button{
    outline: none !important;
  }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main">
       <header>
        <div class="title">
            <h2>Ai Tutor</h2>
        </div>
       </header>
       <main>
        <div class="sectionimg">
            <img src="./bg.png" alt="">
            
        </div>

        <div class="content" >
            <h2>Welcome to AI Tutor, your interactive learning assistant!</h2>
            <h3>Empowering Knowledge Through Conversation</h3>
            <div class="btnsection">
                <a href="#section"><button>Explore</button></a>
            </div>
        </div>
       </main>
       <section id="section">
        <div class="main-content">
            <h2>AI Tutor Chatbot</h2>
            <div class="line"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="sub-content">
            <p>AI Tutor Chatbot offers a seamless, interactive experience for users seeking information and assistance, making learning engaging and efficient with real-time responses and contextual understanding.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sub-content">
            <p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Real-Time Communication:</strong> The chatbot allows users to communicate in real time, providing immediate responses to their queries.</li>
                    <li><strong>Customizable Bot Personality:</strong> The chatbot, named Ai Tutor, is designed to offer helpful and friendly interactions, making it feel like a personal assistant.</li>
                    <li><strong>Contextual Understanding:</strong> The bot maintains context across sessions, ensuring continuity and relevance in conversations.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
            <div class="start">
               <a href="/"> <button>Start Learning</button></a>
            </div>
        </div>
       </section>
       <footer>
        <p>Â© 2024 AI Tutor Chatbot. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
    </div>

</body>
</html>